GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 2nd March, 2005
11 Phalguna, 1926 (S)
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 2nd March,
2005 : -
i)
Shri Shibu Soren relinquished the charge of the office of Minister
of Coal, and
ii)
The Prime Minister assumed the charge of the office of Minister of
Coal.
(K.L. Sharma)
